@startuml m9-composite-liveness-signal-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title M9 — Composite BEAM Liveness Signal

participant "kubelet" as K
participant "/alive\n(composite)" as P
participant "Signal aggregator" as A
participant "BEAM runtime" as B

K -> P: liveness probe
P -> A: composite health?
A -> B: scheduler util, run-queue length,\nmailbox backpressure, restart intensity
B --> A: metrics
A -> A: progress score vs thresholds
alt wedged (queues growing, no throughput)
  A --> K: UNHEALTHY
  note over K #ccffcc: catches "VM alive but wedged"\n=> K8s restarts (a TCP probe would pass)
else making progress
  A --> K: healthy
end
@enduml
